.TH "input_ff_create_memless" 9 "input_ff_create_memless" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
input_ff_create_memless \- create memoryless force-feedback device
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" input_ff_create_memless
.BI "(struct input_dev *dev "  ","
.BI "void *data "  ","
.BI "int (*play_effect)(struct input_dev *, void *, struct ff_effect *) "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
input device supporting force-feedback
.IP "data" 12
driver-specific data to be passed into \fIplay_effect\fP
.IP "play_effect" 12
driver-specific method for playing FF effect
